\id 1TI - Mpoto Bible Version 
\h 1 Timoseo 
\toc1 Baluwa ja kutumbula jaka Paulo kwaka Timoseo 
\toc2 1 Timoseo 
\toc3 1 Timo 
\mt2 Baluwa ja kutumbula jaka Paulo kwaka 
\mt1 Timoseo 
\imt1 Ulongulelo 
\ip Chitabu cha kutumbula chaka Timoseo nde baluwa jejalembakiki na Mtumi Paulo kujenda kwaka mbulwa waki Timoseo. Iwezikana chitabu cha kutumbula chaka Timoseo chakalembakiki pachilanda ja chaka cha 62 mbaka 64 baada ja kubhelakeka Yesu Kristo. Chikahi ambachu iwezikana chakaheghali ujomukelu wa matamu ghaka Paulo. Paulo akabhi na ujonganu wa pambipi namaa na Timoseo, na pamaheli andongalela koni akundowa mwana wake (Filimoni 2:22, 1 Timoseo 1:2,18). 
\ip Baluwa ajeji nde jimu ja baluwa nchechi pachilanda ja baluwa nchechi yaka Paulo ambayu ikalembakiki kwa bhandu bheni, wala nga kwa likanisa. Baluwa yengi itatu nde 2 Timoseo, Tito na Filimoni. Chitabu chaka 1 Timoseo kibhi na malaghalakilu ghamaheli namaa kubhokana na ntundu wa kujojabhela wa likanisa (Sula 2:1-15), ihongozi bha likanisa mobhapalaki kubha (Sula 3:1-13), na malakalilu kubhokana na bhabhola bha upuhe (Sula 1:3-11, 4:1-5, 6:2-5). Baluwa jenu jilangi ntundu Paulo moakabheli ambola Timoseo kubha chiongozi pachilanda ja makanisa. Chitabu cha 1 Timoseo chibhi na malaghalakilu ghamaheli namaa ghaghaweza kubhajangati ihongozi bha likanisa kujendesha mambu gha lihengu la kanisa la pandu pabhajemalela. 
\iot Ghaghabhihomu 
\io1 Paulo atumbu kwa kundamuki Timoseo (Sula 1:1-2). 
\io1 Kabhete Paulo andakali Timoseo kubhokana na bhabhola bha upuhe (Sula 1:3-11). 
\io1 Paulo ajendale kulanda ntundu moanchenguli Yesu Kristo (Sula 1:12-19). 
\io1 Kabhete andandi Timoseo kubhokana na ntundu wa kunjojabhe Chapanga na ihongozi bha likanisa (Sula 2-3). 
\io1 Paulo ajomule baluwa jaki kwa kumpeke Timoseo malaghalakilu ghangi gha kujomulela (Sula 4-6). 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Nepani Paulo, mtumi waka Yesu Kristo kwa amuli jaka Chapanga Mkengalela witu na Bambo Yesu Kristo, joabhi lihobhalelu litu. 
\p  
\v 2 Nukulembe wa Timoseo, mwanangu wa chakaka mu uhobhalelu. 
\p Nukulobhe chihomu, chiha na lukwali, yeihuma kwaka Chapanga Atati witu na Yesu Kristo Bambo witu. 
\s1 Malakalilu kubhokana na mabholu gha upuhe 
\p  
\v 3 Ngati monakakulaghalakile panakabhi nyenda ku Makedonia, mbala utama ku Efeso hoku nahuli ubhahibhalya bhandu bhakumu ngabhibhola mabholu gha upuhe.  
\v 4 Wapwaghila ngabhibhoha chikahi chabhu kwa hadisi ya kuhumbulika na habali ilachu ya akahokolo, ambayu ipelakela bhandu kulochana, wala ngacheichenga lihengu laka Chapanga mu uhobhalelo.  
\v 5 Lengu likolongwa la amuli hajeji nde kuleta upalu, ghouhuma mu mtima unyahi, zamili jambone na uhobhalelu wangakubha na undumila kubheli.  
\v 6 Bhandu bhangi bhahobhiki kuhuma mu mambu aghagha na kung'anambukila malobhi ghangakubha na ndandi.  
\v 7 Bhapala kubha bhabhola bha Shelia, nambu ngachebhaghamanyi mambu ghala ghabhaghalongela wala mambu ghala ghabhaghajomalake kwa uchakaka. 
\p  
\v 8 Tumanyi kubha Shelia nde jambone, ngati mundu anaajitumili kwa indela jejipalika.  
\v 9 Bhelabhela tumanyi kubha Shelia ngechejibhi kwa ndandi jaka mundu wambone, nambu jibhi kwa ndandi ja bhabhaheketa Shelila, bhangakutii, bhangakunjojabhe Chapanga na bhabhabhi na mahoku, bhandu bhangakubha na dini na bhangakubha bhahuhu, bhandu bhabhakoma akatati bhabhu na bhabhakoma akamabhu bhabhu na bhabhakoma bhandu,  
\v 10 na bhakemi, bhalawiti, bhabhajibha bhandu na kubhalombesa kubha ngati bhatumwa, bhapuhe na bhabhalapa kwa upuhe, na lengi lokapi langakujendana na mabholu gha chakaka.  
\v 11 Mabholu aghagha ghapatikana mu Malobhi Manyahi ghaka Chapanga joabhi na ulumbalilu na joapengaleka, ambaghu nepani Paulo mbekiwi nabhatangazya bhandu. 
\s1 Chihomu chaka Chapanga kwaka Paulo 
\p  
\v 12 Nunchengu Kristo Yesu Bambo witu, joakanyeghi makili kwa ndandi akamweni kubha nundongwana, na akanhaghwi nuntumakyaje,  
\v 13 hata ngati pamwande hapa nakabhili nenuntondola jombi, neng'ahika bhandu bhabhunhobhale Kristo, na nenakabhili nundongale mahakau. Nambu Chapanga amonili chiha kwa ndandi nakatendiki bhenibhela kwa ung'ang'a wangu ghonakabhi nau, na kwa kulepalela kubha na uhobhalelu.  
\v 14 Nambu Bambo witu akanyitalili chihomu chaki chamaheli, akambekihi uhobhalelu na upalu ghoubhi kwa kulombana na Kristo Yesu.  
\v 15 Lilobhi lendenu nde lakuhobhaleka, kabhete lipalika kujetakalewa nakanopi: Ja kubha Kristo Yesu akahikiki pundema kubhakengalela bhabhabhi na mahoku. Na nepani mi na mahoku kubhapeta bhokapi.  
\v 16 Nambu Chapanga akamoni chiha, nahuli Yesu Kristo alangihaje uhinakilu ukolongwa kwangu nepani nemi na mahoku kupeta bhokapi, ngubhaje ulenganesu kwa bhala bhabhunhobhalyaje palongi na kupata womi wa mileli.  
\v 17 Henu kwaka Nkolongwa wa mileli, jwangakupotela na jwangakubhonikana, Chapanga kanjika jaki pena, utopelu na ulumbalilu ibya kwaki jombi mileli na mileli! Amina. 
\p  
\v 18 Timoseo wa mwana wangu mu uhobhalelu, nukupekeha amuli ajeji kubhokana na malobhi gha ulota ghaghakalongaliki pamwandi hapa panani jaku. Ughatumilaje malobhi ghanihagha ngati silaha nahuli uweza kukomana ngondo wichu,  
\v 19 ukamulaje uhobhalelu waku na zamili jambone, ambaju bhandu bhangi bhajikangili kutali zamili jabhu, na bhela kuyonanga uhobhalelu wabhu.  
\v 20 Pachilanda ja bhanihabha bhabhi Himenayo na Alekizanda, bhanihabha numpekihi Shetani, nahuli bhabholakikaje bhakotuka kuntondo Chapanga. 
\c 2  
\s1 Malaghalakilu gha kunjojabhe Chapanga 
\p  
\v 1 Kutumbula kwa mambu ghokapi, mumpwaghila Chapanga mambu ghamughapala, mundobha Chapanga, na mubhalobhila bhandu bhangi, na munchengula Chapanga kwa ndandi ja bhandu bhokapi.  
\v 2 Mubhalobhila bhakolongwa na bhandu bhokapi bhabhabhi na lujiniku, nahuli tupata kutama matamu gha kulijeka na gha lukwale, mu uhuhu wokapi na kunjojabhe Chapanga.  
\v 3 Lijambu aleli nde lambone na lunyambiha Chapanga, ambaju nde Mkengalela witu,  
\v 4 joapala bhandu bhokapi bhakengaliwaje na bhaumanya uchakaka.  
\v 5 Kwa ndandi kubhi na Chapanga jumu, na kubhi na jumu joabhajonganesha bhandu na Chapanga, mundu hoju nde Kristo Yesu,  
\v 6 joakalibhohiki mweni ngati nyambiku ja kubhakombola bhandu bhokapi. Ukombola hoghu sajenu ubhonikana kwa chikahi chaki.  
\v 7 Kwa ndandi jeniheji nepani nakahaghuliki kubha mtumi na mbola wa bhandu bha mataifa ghangi, na kubhatangazi bhandu ubholu wa uhobhalelu na uchakaka. Nongela chakaka, na wala ngachengolowa! 
\p  
\v 8 Bhela, kila pandu pamuhimangana kunjojabhe Chapanga, mbala akanalomi bhabhahenga ghamboni kwaka Chapanga bhajinula mabhoku ghabhu bhalobhaje, pangakubha na inyela wala kulochana.  
\v 9 Bhelabhela mbala akambomba bhawataje ingobhu ya utopelu, na bhawata wichu, nga kwa kuloka majunju, wala kulipamba kwa zahabu na lulu wala kwa ingobhu ya mbija yamaheli,  
\v 10 nambu bhabya na matendu ghambone, ngati moibhapalakila akambomba bhabhapwagha kubha bhunjojabhe Chapanga.  
\v 11 Mbomba na alibhola malobhi ghaka Chapanga kwa kutumbala chinunu na kuliheleha.  
\v 12 Nepani ngachenunjetake mbomba kubhola, wala kuntawala mwanalomi, nambu apalika kutama chinunu.  
\v 13 Kwa ndandi Adamu akabhombakiki hoti, na Eva panakatae.  
\v 14 Wala nga Adamu joakakoluwiki, nambu mbomba nde joakakoluwiki na kuheketa Shelia jaka Chapanga.  
\v 15 Hata bhela, mbomba anaakengaliwa kwa kubheleka bhana, ngati anabhajendali kutama mu uhobhalelu na ugholuleku, papamu na mtima wa wambone. 
\c 3  
\s1 Ihongozi mu likanisa 
\p  
\v 1 Lendenu nde lilobhi la kuhobhaleka: Mundu joapala kubha chiongozi wa likanisa, jonihoju atokule lihengu lambone.  
\v 2 Bhela ngacheimpalika chiongozi wa likanisa kubha mundu jobhundongale bhandu liyaha, nambu apalika abyaje na nhwanu waki jumu, abyaje mundu joatemula mambu ghaki wichu, abyaje joalitawala, joatopaleka, joajopale bhandu, joamanya kubhola,  
\v 3 ngaikubha mundu wa kulobhela uwembi, wala joabhi na milomu, nambu abyaje mpole, joapala lukwale, wala ngaikubha mundu wa kupala mbija.  
\v 4 Apalika abyaje mundu joalongo wichu nyumba jaki, joaweza kubhatenda bhana bhaki kubha bhatii kwa utopelu.  
\v 5 Kwa ndandi ngati mundu ngacheamanyi kujilongo nyumba jaki, bho, anaaweza bholi kulighoha likanisa laka Chapanga?  
\v 6 Ngaikubha mundu joanhobhali Kristo henu kateki, ngaahika kulilumbalila na kutemulika ngati Muhakau moakatemulakile.  
\v 7 Kabhete apalika kubha mundu joabhi na luhomu lwambone kwa bhandu bhabhabhi kunja ja likanisa, nahuli ngaihabhuka mu iyoni na chimbenda chaka Muhakau. 
\s1 Bhajangatila mu likanisa 
\p  
\v 8 Bhelabhela bhajangatila mu likanisa bhapalika bhabyaje bhandu bhabhabhi na luhomu lwambone, ngabhikubha akandumila kubheli, ngabhikubha bhandu bhabhalobhela uwembi, wala ngabhikubha bhandu bhabhalipati mbija kwa indela ihakau,  
\v 9 ibhapalika kukamulakila zamili jinyahi kwa uchakaka wa mkati wa uhobhalelu.  
\v 10 Bhanihabha bhapalika bhalengakikaje hoti, na anabhabhonakini kubha bhapalika, bhela, bhatendaje lihengu la ujangatilu.  
\v 11 Bhelabhela bhahanu bhabhu bhapalika bhabyaje na luhomu lwambone, ngabhikubha bhabhaghamba bhandu, nambu bhabyaje bhandu bhabhatemula mambu ghabhu wichu, na bhalongwana kwa ghokapi.  
\v 12 Mjangatila wa likanisa apalika abyaje na nhwanu waki jumu pena, najombi awezaje kulongo bhana bhaki na nyumba jaki wichu.  
\v 13 Kwa ndandi bhajangatila bhabhahenga lihengu labhu wichu bhabhonikana kubha bhambone palongi jaka Chapanga, na bhaweza kulongalela uhobhalelu wabhu ghoubhi muka Kristo Yesu kwa ukangamalu. 
\s1 Sili ngolongwa 
\p  
\v 14 Nukulembela baluwa jenu koni nakahobhalyaje kuhika konihoku henu kateki.  
\v 15 Nambu anangabhakile, mambu ghanakakulembi ghala anaghakujangatya kumanya ntundu moibhapalakila bhandu kujendalela mu Nyumba jaka Chapanga, ambaju nde likanisa laka Chapanga joabhi mwome, nguzu na luhuli lwa chakaka.  
\v 16 Ngachekubhi na choghohi chokapi panani ja uyekuliku wa sili ja uhobhalelu witu ntundu moubheli ukolongwa: 
\q1 Jombi akabhonakini kwa ubhonikanu waka mundu, 
\q1 akamanyakini kubha wambone kwa indela jaka Roho Mhuhu, 
\q1 akabhonakini na bhatumika bha kunani kwaka Chapanga. 
\q1 Akatangizwi kwa bhandu bha inchi yokapi, 
\q1 akahobhaliki pundema pokapi, 
\q1 akatolakiki kunani kwaka Chapanga mu ulumbalilu. 
\c 4  
\s1 Bhabhola bha upuhe 
\p  
\v 1 Roho Mhuhu apwagha hotuhotu ja kubha machobha gha kujomukela bhandu bhangi anabhauleka uhobhalelu, na kujengalela roho yeikolowa, na mabholu gha majobhi.  
\v 2 Mabholu gha ntundu ghonihoghu ghahuma kwa bhandu akandumila kubheli bhabhapwagha upuhe, ambabhu zamili yabhu ibhi ngati ijochakiki kwa choma cha moto.  
\v 3 Bhandu ngati bhanihabha bhabhola kubha nde mahoku kutoghola, na kubhalaghalaki ngabhikula ilebhi yengi. Nambu Chapanga akaibhombiki ilebhi heyi nahuli ijopaliwaje kwa uchengulu na bhabhabhi na uhobhalelu bhabhajimanyi chakaka heji.  
\v 4 Kwa ndandi kila chindu cheabhombiki Chapanga nde chinyahi, wala njeta cha kukanakiwa, ngati anakijopaliwi kwa uchengulu,  
\v 5 maghambu kigholuliki kwa Lilobhi laka Chapanga na kwa kundobha Chapanga. 
\s1 Mtumika wambone waka Kristo Yesu 
\p  
\v 6 Ngati anaubhapwaghi bhahobhalela bhokapi mabholu ghangani, anaubyaje mtumika wambone waka Kristo Yesu, na wibyaje uyobhalile malobhi gha uhobhalelu, na mabholu manyahi ghala ghaujengalile.  
\v 7 Nambu ukanaje hadisi yangakubha ya dini, na yangakubha na ndandi, nanaghu ulibholaje kutama ngati moapali Chapanga.  
\v 8 Kuhenga mazoezi gha ihungu ya hyegha kubhi na nyonjeka pachokope, nambu kuhenga ghala ghaaghapala Chapanga kupalika kwa kila ntundu, ndandi ghabhi na chilanga cha womi wa sajenu, na womi ghola ghowibya panakatae.  
\v 9 Haleli nde lilobhi la chakaka, na lipalika kuhobhaleka nakanopi, na kabhete lipalika kujetakalewa namaa.  
\v 10 Maghambu tuling'aha na kuhenga lihengu nakanopi, kwa ndandi tunhobhalela Chapanga joabhi mwome, joabhi Mkengalela wa bhandu bhokapi, na nakanopi kwa bhala bhabhahobhalela. 
\p  
\v 11 Ubhalaghalakya mambu ghanihagha na kubhabhola mambu ghanihagha.  
\v 12 Ngawijetake mundu jokapi kuujojoha ukombu waku, nambu ubyaje ulenganesu kwa bhabhahobhalela, kwa malobhi ghaku na ntundu moutamila, na mu upalu na uhobhalelu na uhuhu.  
\v 13 Mbaka chikahi panihikaje, ujendalya kukangamala mu kubhasomela Malembu Mahuhu palanga, kubhatangazila na kubhabhola.  
\v 14 Ngawikotoka kutumila nhupu jaka Roho Mhuhu jejibhili mkati jaku, jeupekiwi kwa ulota na pala bhazee pabhakakubheki mabhoku panani jaku na kukulobhela.  
\v 15 Ughaholalya nakanopi mambu ghanihagha ghokapi na ughahengila lihengo, nahuli kujendalela kwaku mu uhobhalelu kubhonikanaje na bhandu bhokapi.  
\v 16 Ulilendaje wamwete, na mabholu ghaku. Ujendalya kuhenga mambu ghanihagha, kwa ndandi kwa kutenda bhenibhela anaulikengalya wamwete, papamu na bhandu bhala bhabhukujowanela. 
\c 5  
\s1 Lihengu kwa bhahobhalela 
\p  
\v 1 Ngaundakalila mwanalomi mzee, nambu ulongila naku ngati atati waku. Ulongila nabhu akakombu ngati bhalongu bhaku,  
\v 2 akambomba bhazee ulongila nabhu ngati akamabhu bhaku, na ulongila na akakamwali ngati bhalombu bhaku, kwa uhuhu wokapi. 
\p  
\v 3 Ubhatopila akambomba bhabhaweliwi na bhalomi na kuhighali panga na mundu wa kubhajangatila.  
\v 4 Nambu anangati mbomba joaweliwi na ndomi abhi na bhana au bhachokolu, bhanihabha bhapalika hoti kulibhola kutenda ghabhapalika kubhajangatila bhalongu bhabhu bhene, na kwa kuhenga bhenibhela bhabhalepa bhazee bhabhu na bhabheleka bhabhu. Kwa ndandi kuhenga bhenibhela kunyambiha Chapanga.  
\v 5 Mbomba jola joaweliwi na ndomi, na kuhighalila kanjika jaki panga kubha na mundu wa kunjangatila, jonihoju abhekiki lihobhalelu laki kwaka Chapanga, na ajendalela kundobha Chapanga ikilu na muhi anjangatyaje.  
\v 6 Nambu mbomba joaweliwi na ndomi joatama kwa utokulelu wa kila ntundu, jonihoju abhi ngati joapotile, hata ngati abhi mwome.  
\v 7 Bhelabhela ubhalaghalakya bhandu mambu ghanihagha, nahuli mundu jokapi ngaabhalongale mahakau.  
\v 8 Nambu anangati mundu jokapi ngacheabhaghoha bhalongu bhaki, na nakanopi bhala bhabhabhi munyumba jaki, mundu jonihoju aukaniki uhobhalelu, kabhete nde muhakau kupeta mundu jwangakuhobhalela. 
\p  
\v 9 Mbomba jokapi joaweliwi na ndomi ngawandemba mu ubhalangiku nambu mbaka abyaje ahikiki hyaka sitini, na ambaju akabhili mbomba waka ndomi jumu pela,  
\v 10 najombi abyaje joakamanyakini kwa matendu ghaki manyahi: Joakabhaleliki bhana bhaki wichu, joakabhajopalile bhaghene panyumba jaki, joakabhagholwili bhandu bhaka Chapanga magholu, joakabhajangatile bhabhabhi na mang'ahiku, na abyaje joakalibhohiki kwa ndandi ja kuhenga matendu ghambone gha kila ntundu. 
\p  
\v 11 Nambu akambomba bhabhaweliwi na bhalomi bhabhabhi akakamwale ngaubhabheka mu ubhalangiku ghonihoghu, maghambu utokulelu wabhu wa kihyegha anaubhapaliki kutoghuleka kabhete anakubhatenda bhundeka Kristo,  
\v 12 bhela anabhabyaje na mahoku kwa ndandi bhaulekiki uhobhalelu wabhu wa kutumbula.  
\v 13 Bhelabhela akambomba bhabhaweliwi na bhalomi ngati bhanihabha bhalibhola kubha bhakata koni bhakapetaje nyumba kwa nyumba, wala ngachebhakubha bhakata pela, nambu bhelabhela bhalijingiha mu mambu ambaghu nga ghabhu, na kulongela malobhi ghangakubhapalika kulongela.  
\v 14 Bhela mbala akambomba bhabhaweliwi na bhalomi, ambabhu nga bhazee, bhatoghulikaje, bhabhelaka bhana na kuighoha nyumba yabhu, nahuli ngabhumpekeha adui mbekenyu ja kulongela mambu mahakau panani jitu.  
\v 15 Kwa ndandi akambomba bhangi bhabhaweliwi na bhalomi bhajomwi kujileka indela jaka Chapanga na kunjengale Shetani.  
\v 16 Nambu anangati mbomba jokapi joanhobhali Kristo anaabhi na akambomba bhabhaweliwi na bhalomi munyumba jaki, jombi apalika abhajangatya mwene, nahuli likanisa liwezaje kubhajangati bhala ambabhu nde bhabhaweliwi na bhalomi na kuhighali kanjika panga na mundu wa kubhajangatila. 
\p  
\v 17 Ihongozi bhabhajemale wichu mu likanisa bhapalika kupekewa utopelu mala pabhele, na nakanopi bhala ambabhu lihengu labhu nde kubhatangazi bhandu na kubhabhola Lilobhi laka Chapanga.  
\v 18 Kwa ndandi Malembu Mahuhu ghapwagha, “Ngaujikonga ng'ombi ndomu pajihenga lihengu la kupumunda mponga.” Bhelabhela ghapwagha, “Muhenga lihengu apalika kupekewa malepu ghaki.”  
\v 19 Ngawijetakela kujopalela matakilu panani jaka mzee, nambu kwa ulandilu wa bhandu bhabhele au bhatatu.  
\v 20 Bhandu bhala bhabhajendalela kutenda mahoku ubhalakalyaje palongi ja bhandu bhokapi, nahuli na bhandu bhangi bhajoghupaje. 
\p  
\v 21 Nukulaghalaki wenga palongi jaka Chapanga na palongi jaka Kristo Yesu, na palongi ja bhatumika bhahaghulika, ughakamula malaghalakilu ghanihagha ghokapi, kabhete ngawitemula kwa manyata, wala ngawitenda lilobhi lokapi kwa kujeghamake upambala ghumo.  
\v 22 Ngawijombateka kumbekela mundu mabhoku, wala ngawishiliki mahoku gha bhandu bhangi. Ulilendaje wamwete na utamaje kwa kunyambiha Chapanga. 
\p  
\v 23 Ngawikunywa machi kanjika jaki, nambu ukunywa na divai pachokopi kwa ndandi ja lutumbu lwako, na itamu yeyukupata pamaheli. 
\p  
\v 24 Mahoku gha bhandu bhangi ghabhonikana hotuhotu, naghombi ghabhalongulela ku utemulo, nambu mahoku gha bhandu bhangi ghabhajengale kunyuma jabhu.  
\v 25 Bhelabhela, matendu ghambone ghabhonikana hotuhotu, na hata ghala ghangakubhonikana palanga ngacheghaweza kuhiyakika. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Bhatumwa bhokapi bhapalika kubhatii akabambo bhabhu, nahuli bhandu ngabhalitondola lihina laka Chapanga na mabholu ghito.  
\v 2 Bhatumwa ambabhu akabambo bhabhu nde bhandu bhabhunhobhale Kristo, ngabhajojoha maghambu bhabhona bhombi ngati bhalongu, nambu ipalika bhabhatumakyaje wichu nakanopi, kwa ndandi bhombi bhapata nyonjeka kubhokana na lihengu labhu nde bhahobhalela ambabhu nde bhapalakika nabhu. 
\s1 Mabholu gha upuhe na kujoloka hindu kwa chakaka 
\p Mambu ghanihagha ughabholaje na kughalakalila.  
\v 3 Mundu jokapi anaabholiki mabholu ghangi, wala ngacheaghajetakela malobhi gha womi ghaka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo, na kutama ngati moapali Chapanga,  
\v 4 jonihoju atenda kulilumbalila, wala ngachealimanyi lilobhi lokapi. Abhi na mangongo gha kuholalela mambu gha malalukilu, mashindanu gha malobhi, ambaghu mu ghanihagha kupita wihu, milomu, matondu, na kubhaholalela bhandu bhangi mahakau,  
\v 5 na kulochana kwanga na ujomukelu kokupita kwa bhandu bhabhayonangiki malangu ghabhu, bhabhajikosiki chakaka, bhombi bhaholake kuntumaki Chapanga nde indela ja kulipati mbija. 
\p  
\v 6 Nambu kuhenga mambu ghala ghaaghapala Chapanga papamu na kujetengane na ntundu momelile nde nyonjeka ngolongwa.  
\v 7 Kwa ndandi ngachetukahikiki panu pundema na chindu chokapi, kabhete ngachetuweza kubhoka panu pundema na chindu chokapi.  
\v 8 Nambu anatubhili na chilebhi na ingobhu, itupalika kutosheka na hindu yeniheyi.  
\v 9 Nambu bhala bhabhapala kubha na hindu yamaheli bhahabhuka mu malengakeku, na kutangila mu chimbenda cha utokulelu uhakau na wa king'ang'a, na kubhahabhuha bhandu mu kuhobha na kuyonangeka.  
\v 10 Kwa ndandi kupala nakanopi mbija nde utumbulilu wa uhakau wokapi. Bhandu bhangi bhatokulili namaa mbija mbaka bhalekini na uhobhalelu, na kulijocha mitima jabhu kwa mabhinilu ghamaheli kwa ghala ghabhahenga. 
\s1 Paulo andaghalaki Timoseo 
\p  
\v 11 Nambu wehapa, wa mundu waka Chapanga, ughatilaje mambu ghanihagha ghokapi. Ukangamalaje kutama wichu, utamaje ngati moapali Chapanga, ubya na uhobhalelu, upalu, uhinakilu na upole.  
\v 12 Ukomanaje wichu ngondu yela ya uhobhalelu. Ukamulaje womi wa mileli ghowalowakakile na Chapanga pala paukahobhali uhobhalelu waku unyahi palongi ja bhalandilu bhamaheli.  
\v 13 Nukulaghalaki palongi jaka Chapanga joayipeke hindu yokapi womi, na palongi jaka Kristo Yesu joakabhohiki ulandilu na kupwagha mweni uchakaka kwa ndomu waki palongi jaka Pontio Pilato,  
\v 14 ukamulaje amuli jenjenu panga na mahakau, wala mahoku, mbaka Lichobha lela la kubhonikana kwaka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo.  
\v 15 Yesu anaapitalya mu chikahi chekibhekakiki na Chapanga, jombi joalumbalike, joabhi kanjika jaki Mtawala, Nkolongwa wa bhakolongwa, na Bambo wa mabambo.  
\v 16 Jombi kanjika jaki nde ngacheapotela, atami mu unang'anu ambau njeta mundu joaweza kuheghalela. Njeta mundu joalabhalile kumbona au joaweza kumbona. Utopelu na uweza ubhi najombi mileli! Amina. 
\p  
\v 17 Ubhalaghalakyaje bhandu bhala bhabhabhi na hindu yamaheli bha pundema ghoni sajenu bhakotukaje kulibhona, wala ngabhibheka lihobhalelu labhu mu hindu ambayu nga ya kuhobhaleka, nambu bhabhekaje lihobhalelu labhu muka Chapanga ambaju atupekeha hindu yokapi kwa maheli nahuli tuitumilaje kwa chiheku.  
\v 18 Ubhalaghalakyaje bhatendaje ghambone, bhabyaje na hindu yamaheli kwa kutenda matendu ghambone, bhabyaje na mtima wa kubhoha nakanope, na kushiliki na bhandu bhangi hindu yabhu.  
\v 19 Na kwa kuhenga bhenibhela anabhalibhekilaje chikoku chibyaje luhuli lunyahi kwa chikahi chechihika, nahuli bhapataje womi ghoubhi wa chakaka. 
\p  
\v 20 Wenga Timoseo, ughalendaje wichu ghokapi ghala ghaupekiwi, ulijepaje na malobhi gha kindema, na ghangakubha na ndandi jokapi jela, na malochanu ambaghu kwa upuhe ghaghalowakeka kwa upuhe “Umanyi.”  
\v 21 Kwa ndandi bhandu bhangi bhahobhalili umanyi hoghu na kwa kuhenga bhenibhela bhaulekiki uhobhalelu. 
\p Chihomu chaka Chapanga chibyaje na mwehapa mabhokapi. Amina.